# QUICK SETUP CHECKLIST
# ============================================
#
# [ ] 1. Revoke old Stripe keys (CRITICAL)
# [ ] 2. Generate new Stripe keys
# [ ] 3. Sign up for Resend
# [ ] 4. Verify domain in Resend
