# ============================================
# SECURITY BEST PRACTICES
# ============================================
#
# ✅ DO:
# - Use different keys for dev/staging/production
# - Rotate keys every 3-6 months
# - Use strong random keys (crypto.randomBytes)
# - Keep service account JSON secure
# - Monitor Stripe webhook signatures
#
# ❌ DON'T:
# - Commit real keys to git
# - Share keys in Slack/email
# - Use same keys across environments
# - Hardcode keys in source code
# - Reuse exposed/compromised keys
#
# ============================================


# ============================================
# TESTING LOCALLY
# ============================================
#
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Fill in all values
# 3. Run: npm install
# 4. Run: npm run dev
# 5. Test: http://localhost:5173
#
# Note: .env.local is gitignored automatically
#
# ============================================


# ============================================
# TROUBLESHOOTING
# ============================================
#
# Problem: "Stripe checkout not working"
# Solution: Check STRIPE_SECRET_KEY starts with sk_live_
#           Verify webhook secret is correct
#
# Problem: "Emails not sending"
# Solution: Verify domain in Resend dashboard
#           Check RESEND_API_KEY is valid
#           Look at Resend logs for delivery status
#
# Problem: "Firebase permission denied"
# Solution: Check Firestore security rules
#           Verify service account JSON is valid
#           Ensure user is authenticated
#
# Problem: "Affiliate links missing partner ID"
# Solution: Redeploy after adding VITE_ variables
#           Clear browser cache
#           Check URL has ?partner= parameter
#
# ============================================


